<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3147576" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="4">The table view and form view reflect the same data. Changes made in the table are also visible in the form, and changes to the form are visible in the table.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3153748" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="5">If there are several logical forms in a document, the table is only able to show one at a time.<comment>UFI removed two paras, see #60894</comment></paragraph>
